data.title: TAURUS 65 357MAG/ .38SP 4IN 6RD SS FXS
data.meta_description: Taurus Model 65 revolvers are a longtime favorite of security personnel and perfect for Homeland Defense Forces. This medium-frame, 6-shot revolver features comfortable rubber grips and a deep, lustrous finish. This single action/double action 357 Magnum has a 4" barrel and fixed sights. It has a transfer bar safety and the Taurus Security System This model has a matte stainless steel metal finish.
data.text:
Taurus Model 65 revolvers are a longtime favorite of security personnel and perfect for Homeland Defense Forces. This medium-frame, 6-shot revolver features comfortable rubber grips and a deep, lustrous finish. This single action/double action 357 Magnum has a 4" barrel and fixed sights. It has a transfer bar safety and the Taurus Security System This model has a matte stainless steel metal finish.
